{"tid":1219404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"送給所有義士︰《家明》－謝安琪","createTime":"2019-06-13T20:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T12:06:05.000Z","uid":23854,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d04d8becb15186f57cbf398421fb4aa25c56e9d3","tid":1219404,"uid":23854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:02:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_K_qrFYozkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_K_qrFYozkg&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=3ac404ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_K_qrFYozkg</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完一人一張撼動人心既圖果個post之後咁岩聽到《家明》呢首歌，個mv係雨革version，我覺得，6月9日至12日出過黎、亦會繼續再出黎既所有義士，都值得用呢首歌去紀念。<br />\n<br />\n我地不願具名亦不敢具名，就當每一個人都係家明。<br />\n我地一齊就係熱愛自由既家明。<br />\n<br />\n利申：所有相片影片來自網絡／討論區／各大傳媒，所有credit都係佢地既"},{"pid":"4460b6e8a7479cd9886d165fcdd999ed2bae9844","tid":1219404,"uid":23854,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:38:08.000Z","msg":"（善心打破自己零回覆）<br />\n<br />\n我自己都係發夢有份係6月12出黎既人，其實我好驚，好怕，同我傾過出唔出好既所有朋友都係。<br />\n驚，但都要做。<br />\n<br />\n我想借呢首歌、呢條片話比所有其他人知，我地只係一班怕事但依然願意為自由而犧牲既人。<br />\n<br />\n好多謝大家願意成為我既同路人。"},{"pid":"698aa8612c8908209c9f3f43554fd451b97a842c","tid":1219404,"uid":145758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:42:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d509555311c02bf7c56f59d92344477b821c750","tid":1219404,"uid":23854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698aa8612c8908209c9f3f43554fd451b97a842c","tid":1219404,"uid":145758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:42:39.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:46:55.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推比更多人睇到，即使我地不露臉不留名，歷史上一定會有我地既痕跡！"},{"pid":"3f62aba1bf66086d71a78ff0101d295a4d29c473","tid":1219404,"uid":9394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:50:59.000Z","msg":"呢首歌我聽到喊左好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif